    "m_Title": "Sample Material In Custom Function",
    "m_Content": "Using custom function to only calculate what is enabled by the user, better performance\n\nAlso easier to do the same calculations for multiple sub-materials, this material is way too complicated for its own good\n\nComments in hlsl file if you want to step through it\n\nIf only we could have arrays.....",
